/chinese-law","type":"heading","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law#参考资料","content":"参考资料"},"54":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-2","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"中国大陆的法律体系，按照效力位阶，可大致分为以下几个层级：宪法、法律、行政法规、地方性法规、规章。宪法是根本大法，具有最高的法律效力，其他法律都不能与宪法相抵触。\n以下是具体层级及其制定机关："},"55":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-3","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"宪法:\n《中华人民共和国宪法》是国家的根本大法，是其他一切法律的立法依据和基础。"},"56":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-4","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"法律:\n由全国人民代表大会(全国人大)及其常务委员会制定，如《中华人民共和国民法典》、《中华人民共和国刑法》等。"},"57":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-5","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"行政法规:\n由国务院制定，是对法律的具体化和补充，如《中华人民共和国食品安全法实施条例》。"},"58":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-6","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"地方性法规:\n由省级和设区的市级人民代表大会及其常务委员会制定，在各自的行政区域内施行，如《上海市生活垃圾管理条例》。"},"59":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-7","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","content":"规章:\n包括部门规章和地方政府规章，部门规章由国务院各部委制定，地方政府规章由地方各级人民政府制定。\n此外，还有一些特殊类型的法律，如自治条例和单行条例，它们在民族自治地方和经济特区具有特殊法律地位。法律效力层级的高低，决定了在具体适用法律时的优先顺序，下位法必须服从上位法。"},"60":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-8","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law#参考资料","content":"中华人民共和国法律位阶 - 维基百科"},"61":{"id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law-9","page_id":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law","type":"text","url":"/notes/civil-service/chinese-law#参考资料","content":"法律位阶 - 百度百科"},"62":{"id":"/notes/civil-service","page_id":"/notes/civil-service","type":"page","content":"行测笔记","url":"/notes/civil-service"},"63":{"id":"/notes/coding","page_id":"/notes/coding","type":"page","content":"Hello Code!","url":"/notes/coding"},"64":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"page","content":"认识数据库","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse"},"65":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-0","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据","content":"数据"},"66":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-1","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库","content":"数据库"},"67":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-2","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库系统","content":"数据库系统"},"68":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-3","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库管理系统","content":"数据库管理系统"},"69":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-4","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"heading","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#结论","content":"结论"},"70":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-5","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","content":"数据库中常见的基本概念如下。"},"71":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-6","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据","content":"数据是对客观事物、事件的记录与描述，也是对客观事物的逻辑归纳。数据可以是连续的，如声音、图像等，也可以是离散的，如符号、文字等。"},"72":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-7","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库","content":"数据库（Database，DB）是存储在计算机内、有组织的、可共享的相关数据的集合，这种集合按一定的数据模型组织、描述并长期存储，同时能够以安全可靠的方法对数据进行检索。"},"73":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-8","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库系统","content":"数据库系统（Database System，DBS）是指在计算机系统中引入数据库后的系统。它主要由数据库、数据库用户、计算机硬件系统和计算机软件系统（含数据库管理系统）等几部分组成。"},"74":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-9","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库管理系统","content":"数据库管理系统（Database Management System，DBMS）是指建立、运用、管理和维护数据库，并对数据库进行统一控制的系统软件。"},"75":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-10","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#数据库管理系统","content":"常见的数据库管理系统有 SQL Server、Oracle、MySQL、Access等。"},"76":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-11","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#结论","content":"Data < DB < DBMS < DBS"},"77":{"id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse-12","page_id":"/notes/coding/learn-databse","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/learn-databse#结论","content":"注意：DBMS 是 DBS 的必要组成部分，没有 DBMS 的 DBS 在实际中是不存在的。"},"78":{"id":"/notes/coding/package-json","page_id":"/notes/coding/package-json","type":"page","content":"什么是 package.json","url":"/notes/coding/package-json"},"79":{"id":"/notes/coding/package-json-0","page_id":"/notes/coding/package-json","type":"text","url":"/notes/coding/package-json","content":"package.json 是 npm 等前端包管理器生成的一份文件，其中包含许多元信息。"},"80":{"id":"/notes/grad-school","page_id":"/notes/grad-school","type":"page","content":"专业课笔记","url":"/notes/grad-school"},"81":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration","type":"page","content":"集成 Fuma Comment 的笔记","url":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration"},"82":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration#-fuma-comment-集成到文档站点指南","content":"📚 Fuma Comment 集成到文档站点指南"},"83":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration#-核心文件清单","content":"🎯 核心文件清单"},"84":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration-2","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration","type":"heading","url":"/notes/geek-lab/fuma-comment-integration#-1